HEADWORD: Hypocraterimorphous
<hw>Hyp`o*cra*ter`i*mor"phous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[Pref. <ets>hypo-</ets> + Gr. <grk>krath`r</grk> bowl +
